      "comment": "JAZZMATIC (7) is a Robert Mowat-trained newcomer by Tommy Shelby out of Jemima Rocks. Start all important and will need some luck getting across from the wide draw. Has a nice profile and expected to measure up at first outing. INDIAN PRINCE (4) stalked lead from an outside box last start before finishing third (26.12) at Geelong in a Maiden over 460m. Leading player again. LITTLE RAT (8) has been mixing form lately, hitting the frame two back before finishing fifth (31.24) at this track in a Maiden FIN. Well placed here and can atone this time. DRIP DRIP (5) cannot be left out despite racing here for the first time.",
